Syndromicity analysis

Analysis for syndromicity based on several factors: - whether a disease contains syndrome in the name? - the amount of genes associated to different branches?

As of 30 July, there is no clear correlation between the syndromicity and the number of tissues either way

Parsed with column specification:
cols(
  orphaID = col_character(),
  label = col_character(),
  genes = col_character(),
  n_genes = col_double(),
  description = col_character(),
  roots = col_character()
)
